refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Imagick Imagick::evaluateImages intevaluate
Applies an arithmetic operator pixel-by-pixel across all images in the sequence, reducing the stack to a single image. This can, for example, compute the pixelwise mean, sum, minimum, or maximum of the images.

&reftitle.parameters;
evaluate
One of the Imagick::EVALUATE_* constants specifying the operator to apply across the sequence.

&reftitle.returnvalues;

 Returns a new Imagick object containing the single
 resulting image.
